product.title: VEVOR 32.25 in. x 1 in. Deck Balusters Staircase Baluster Staircase Iron Baluster Wave Arc Baluster for Outdoor (51-Pack)
product.description: These VEVOR metal deck balusters are a great choice to update your deck or stair. Black powder-coated iron last through the years, even exposure outdoor environment. Thanks to the pre-drilled holes and screws, they are easy to install. You can enjoy your secure and beautiful deck with our railing balusters.
feature_bullets: Black powder coating improves weather resistance
Pre-drilled and self-tapping screws are easy to assemble
descriptive_attributes: High-quality iron material: our deck balusters are constructed with durable iron material, warp-proof, rust-proof and corrosion-proof for long-term usage, the sturdy metal material can efficiently improve the security of your deck

51-pack 32.25 in. L: these metal deck spindles measure 32.25 in./82 cm L and 1 in./2.5 cm W that will fit for most railing frames, we provide you 51 balusters here and you can choose the quantity according to the dimension of your deck or staircase

Stylish deck balusters: wave curved shape and matte black color will create a beautiful deck or porch railing for you, our metal balusters are powder-coated with AAMA-2604 compliant material that can keep stable under various weather conditions

Convenient installation: the staircase balusters feature pre-drilled holes at both ends for your easy and quick installation, with 204 self-tapping screws, the balusters can be effortlessly connected with wooden or metal frames

Wide application: the balusters are widely used outdoor or indoor, suitable for deck, stair, porch railing, yard, balcony and other places that need fence protection, it is compatible with wood and composite deck
Balusters are made of iron material that is high-quality and sturdy enough for long service life, there is no worry about the quality
Including 51 balusters, each baluster is 32.25 in./82 cm L and 1 in./2.5 cm W the size of them is appropriate and the amount is enough
Black powder-coated surface plays a decorative role, besides, it can improve the weathering resistance ability of the balusters
Balusters are designed with curved wave shape, modern and stylish for your deck, they are both practical and ornamental
With the pre-drilled holes and self-tapping screws, there is no need to worry about the assembly, it will cost you less time to install the balusters
Package content: 51 x deck baluster 204 x screws
